&lt;p&gt;Grayscale Investments is seeking a Senior AI Security Architect to partner with our AI Enablement squad and broader engineering organization to ensure the safe, controlled adoption of AI across the firm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for designing and implementing security controls, guardrails, and governance mechanisms for AI-enabled systems, including LLM-based applications, agentic workflows, and AI-assisted development practices. This role is a key part of ensuring that AI evolves from experimentation into a secure, auditable, and scalable capability.&lt;/p&gt;
